<li>A listing of all the Player Characters and major Non-Player Characters in the Kitaran Sea Region.</li>
<li class="c4"><br />
Also, information known to the players, such as the <a href="story/index.html">Players' Story</a> is here.</li>
</ul><b><a href="world.html">World Information</a></b>
<ul>
